citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1250 on
24-Jul-19.
Upon arrival at the facility contact was made with the licensee's spouse. She stated that the licensee was not
home. She was also unavailable for inspection.
End of report.
